name: SUPER MEGA COMBO BAD LUCK
description: Good luck and bad luck are two sides of the same coin. What bad luck for one, good luck for another. The herbivore dies, so that the predator could live. Is it good or bad luck?  The "SUPER MEGA COMBO BAD LUCK" package includes:  1. Old rusty Horseshoe (with the ends pointing down) 2. Number of the beast (666) 3. Broken mirror 4. Chinese character for failure disaster (zāinàn) 5. Inverted cross 6. Number 4 7. Сhernobog rune (rune of death) 8. Pentacle 9. Skull 10. Number 13
